    <h2>Choose Your Share</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="lead">Buy a quarter, a half, or a whole. The more you take, the better the price per pound &mdash; and you get the premium cuts at the whole-animal average, not meat-counter sticker prices.</p>
