    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="lead">Sandhills Cattle Procurement is building a rail-served sale barn and butcher right where the cattle are — so the value stays in the community instead of shipping out. A working market, a local butcher, freezer beef for families, and a cleaner, calmer way to move cattle.</p>
    <div class="grid" style="margin-top:46px;">
      <div class="feat">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <div><h3>The Sale Barn on the Rails</h3><p>A market where producers get a fair shake and buyers come from miles around — sitting right on the line, built for the future of cattle movement.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <div><h3>The Local Butcher</h3><p>Custom processing and freezer beef for the community next door — the quality meat counter this country deserves.</p></div>
      </div>
